title: Black Cards - Use Your Disillusion
description:
Use Your Disillusion EP (plus some extra tracks) by Black Cards, released July 2012.
I saw there were no torrents for this EP so I decided to get all the tracks together and create my own for anyone interested. Sorry if the quality is shitty, they're mostly collected fromAlso, I'm sorry for the quality of Dirty Little Fingerprints, as I was unable to find a better quality version.

Track Listing:
1. Wolf Slayer
2. End of Pretend feat. Matthew Koma
3. F.T.W.
4. Talk Dirty feat. Amba Shepherd
5. Club Called Heaven (Bonus)
6. Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Fame (Bonus)
7. Dirty Little Fingerprints (Live) (Bonus)

If you have any requests for any more Black Cards songs, or just anything from anyone, let me know!

Thanks for the DL,
Boonsy.
